steps.name: Click on the 'Contacts' page from the sidebar menu
Click on the 'Clients' tab in the sub menu
Click on the first commercial contact from the 'Commercial clients' table
Click on the 'Email' button from the Contact landing page
Enter the subject of the letter into the 'Subject' input field
Enter the text into the Email
